### **4. 40_StreamChartBlade**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes live numeric data in a sharp, fast-scrolling blade-style animated chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamChartBlade - Realtime Data Stream Visualizer

StreamChartBlade offers a clean blade-style scrolling chart for displaying realtime metric feeds or sensor data.

## Features
- Smooth live scrolling  
- Adjustable refresh interval  
- Matplotlib-based  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/40_StreamChartBlade.git
cd 40_StreamChartBlade
python visualize.py
